```
Some `code`
.
<p>Some <code>code</code></p>
```

```
Some `code
with a line break`
.
<p>Some <code>code
with a line break</code></p>
```

```
Special characters: `*hi*`
.
<p>Special characters: <code>*hi*</code></p>
```

```
*foo`*`
.
<p>*foo<code>*</code></p>
```

```````
`````a`a``a```a````a``````a`````
.
<p><code>a`a``a```a````a``````a</code></p>
```````

```
` ``a`` `
.
<p><code>``a``</code></p>
```

Space stripping with multi-backtick delimiters (spec: "If the content
starts or ends with a backtick character, a single space is removed"):

```
`` `foo` ``
.
<p><code>`foo`</code></p>
```

Implicitly closed by end of paragraph:

```
` a
c
.
<p><code> a
c</code></p>
```

Inline attributes attach to the code element:

```
`code`{.a}
.
<p><code class="a">code</code></p>
```

```
`code`{key="value"}
.
<p><code key="value">code</code></p>
```
